## Development Workflow

### Branch Naming

Follow this pattern:

```bash
feature/add-candidate-form-frontend    # New feature
bugfix/form-validation-frontend        # Bug fix
refactor/component-reorganization      # Refactoring
```

Add `-frontend` suffix to avoid conflicts with backend work.

### Development Scripts

```bash
npm start                   # Start development server (port 3000)
npm test                    # Run tests
npm run test:coverage       # Run tests with coverage report
npm run build              # Production build
npm run lint               # Run ESLint
```

### Coding Standards

- **English only**: All code, comments, and text must be in English
- **Consistent formatting**: Use Prettier for auto-formatting
- **Linting**: All files must pass ESLint checks
- **Tests**: All new features must have tests with >80% coverage

